snippet.title: SlasherRPG - Official Trailer EP 1
snippet.description:
Slasher RPG, Fantasy Openworld style game, grow vegetables, crafting building and action adventures in a wide world.Content mix : farming, pet breeding, dungeon exploration, crafting and combat. and the possibilities are endless. Along with stories and interesting things that are waiting for you to explore.
